  "texts": [
    "The performance of the three prediction models for each subgroup was compared using C-index and IBS.",
    "The metadata model achieved C-indexes of 0.700-0.711 and IBSs of 0.261-0.328 in predicting progression to any grade of DR, referable DR and VTDR in the internal dataset.",
    "Compared with the metadata model, C-indexes of the fundus model improved to 0.826 (95% CI, d, Visual diagram of the DeepDR Plus system.",
